      <title>基辅确认了其所称的俄罗斯影子石油船队中的油轮的身份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/kyiv-identifies-238-ships-it-says-are-in-russia-s-shadow-fleet-of-oil-tankers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰确认了这 238 艘油轮属于俄罗斯用来在全球范围内运输石油和燃料的影子舰队，目的是让西方当局对这些运输船实施制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/kyiv-identifies-238-ships-it-says-are-in-russia-s-shadow-fleet-of-oil-tankers</guid>
