    <item>
      <title>丹麦将利率下调四分之一个百分点以维护货币挂钩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/denmark-cuts-rate-by-quarter-point-to-defend-currency-peg</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹麦央行跟随欧洲央行将利率下调四分之一个百分点，以维护瑞典克朗与共同货币的挂钩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/denmark-cuts-rate-by-quarter-point-to-defend-currency-peg</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 16:02:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非希望二十国集团重新考虑穷国的债务成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/south-africa-wants-g-20-rethink-of-poor-nations-debt-costs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非财政部长埃诺克·戈东瓦纳 (Enoch Godongwana) 表示，南非希望二十国集团重新评估四年前建立的重组穷国债务的体系，因为该体系没有充分考虑这些国家的债务负担。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/south-africa-wants-g-20-rethink-of-poor-nations-debt-costs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 16:00:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥尔萨格称特朗普准备结束“大即坏”的并购观点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-12/orszag-says-trump-poised-to-end-big-is-bad-view-of-m-a-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Lazard Inc. 首席执行官 Peter Orszag 表示，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普任命的监管官员标志着拜登政府对并购的“大即坏”观点的终结。他在“彭博未平仓合约”上表示，进入 2025 年，交易环境“看起来非常有利”。Sonali Basak 的华尔街快讯将于周五发布。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-12/orszag-says-trump-poised-to-end-big-is-bad-view-of-m-a-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 15:19:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国对冲基金创始人因涉嫌 13 亿美元税务诈骗在丹麦被判入狱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/british-hedge-fund-founder-sanjay-shah-jailed-over-cum-ex-scam-in-denmark</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国对冲基金交易员桑杰·沙阿因策划了一起价值 10 亿美元的税务诈骗案被丹麦法官判处 12 年监禁，这是迄今为止欧洲庞大的 Cum-Ex 交易丑闻中判处的最重监禁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/british-hedge-fund-founder-sanjay-shah-jailed-over-cum-ex-scam-in-denmark</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 15:11:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
