      <title>巴西鹰派加息未能阻止市场抛售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/brazil-s-real-climbs-on-central-bank-s-hawkish-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易员们将巴西央行的鹰派立场称为“震慑”举措，将提振该国受创的资产。一天后，市场发出信号称这还不够。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/brazil-s-real-climbs-on-central-bank-s-hawkish-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 12:15:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝恩不顾政府禁令重返南非</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/bain-makes-south-african-comeback-bid-despite-government-ban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝恩公司因腐败丑闻被禁止与南非政府做生意长达十年，目前该公司正试图通过免费承接一个私人项目来挽回其在南非的声誉。]]></description>
